{"tid":1354053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你係朱凱廸，你會點樣應付何君堯依啲無賴","createTime":"2019-07-23T05:24:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T06:37:46.000Z","uid":89185,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2d52714475c3b16e395ec8c8e33e352a7d928e4e","tid":1354053,"uid":89185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:24:12.000Z","msg":"我唔會畀佢spin咗去講光復行動，我一定死咬住佢煽動白衫人打無辜市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本唔洗反駁佢每一句，條友無賴至極咩都講得出。<br />\n我係朱凱廸嘅話，就一定不斷對住鏡頭講依條無賴妖言惑眾，煽動元朗鄉親，散播假新聞，令到鄉親誤以為真係有人燒村搞佢地祖墳，令佢地打傷無辜市民，甚至依家真係搞到有人話要去燒佢地村搞佢地祖墳，所有惡果都係何君堯依個賤人搞出黎，無風起浪！<br />\n只要死咬住依一點，何君堯依條無賴就無辦法spin去第二度，亦可以將焦點集中返係條無賴度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真，做議員嗰班，你地一定要好好利用大氣電波嘅珍貴時間，你地係最多機會被採訪嘅人，你地搞唔掂建制班無賴，落於下風，點樣製造輿論壓力？做好自己份內事啦！"},{"pid":"68ffc6b4211354793371a74a2f0ace8612eb21f7","tid":1354053,"uid":89185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:24:21.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"16d1c927e40c9be5d5606abd20554eb2629f5f9d","tid":1354053,"uid":34415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/520eo1h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F520eo1h.jpg&h=32ecfa79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMbASUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMbASUF.jpg&h=a2ce6deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kjPbreK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkjPbreK.jpg&h=068b8664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKrX6eR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKrX6eR.jpg&h=922f47ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/87OcaGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src